<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأمثلة:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١- قُمْتُ بنصيبِي منَ العَمَل أَوْ بنصيبيَ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَمَوْتُ بِآدابي أَوْ بِآدَابيَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَعْطِفُ عَلَى الْفَقِيرِ بِصَدَقَاتِي أَوْ بِصَدَقَاتِي.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>